AutoClick - Desktop Macro Recorder
====================================
Version: 1.0.0
License: MIT
Homepage: https://github.com/CrisTecnica/autoclick

AutoClick records and plays back mouse and keyboard macros
with adjustable speed, infinite loop, and global hotkeys.

Global Hotkeys:
  F9  - Start recording
  F10 - Stop recording
  F11 - Play macro
  F12 - Stop everything
  Esc - Emergency stop

Launch: autoclick
